[
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_2",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "picture",
    "bbox": [
      0.40861776809489225,
      0.05822120673605822,
      0.5940450254175744,
      0.18684945417618684
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_0",
    "text": "广",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08908254659888647,
      0.07345349919607345,
      0.12781408859840232,
      0.1716171617161716
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_5",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.8729121278140886,
      0.07446898536007447,
      0.9150326797385621,
      0.1766945925361767
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_3",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6274509803921569,
      0.07954641618007954,
      0.859840232389252,
      0.152999915376153
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_1",
    "text": "“十一五”时期，交通运输行业深入贯 彻科学发展观，坚决落实党中央提出的 “保增长、保民生、保稳定”的要求，围绕做 好“三个服务”（服务国民经济和社会发展 全局，服务社会主义新农村建设，服务人 民群众安全便捷出行),加快基础设施建 设，努力提高运输服务水平，积极应对国 际金融危机影响，基础设施建设成就显 著，网络更趋完善，运输服务水平明显提 升，安全应急保障能力明显增强，“十一 五”规划确定的目标任务全面完成，成为 新中国成立以来，交通运输发展速度最 快、发展质量最好、服务水平提升最显著 的时期，为保持经济社会平稳较快发展做 出了积极贡献。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14185427257322683,
      0.07988491156807989,
      0.3747276688453159,
      0.16484725395616484
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_4",
    "text": "交通运输部部长李盛霖",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6753812636165577,
      0.15401540154015403,
      0.8370854514645364,
      0.16484725395616484
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_6",
    "text": "标志性变化",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.020334059549745823,
      0.2311923500042312,
      0.1476640038731542,
      0.25184056867225185
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_7",
    "text": "一个主题：科学发展有效提升“三个服务\"的能力和水平。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.61679980634229,
      0.23525429466023526,
      0.8506414911643669,
      0.24947110095624947
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_8",
    "text": "■速公路建设连续迈上新台阶 ■全国所有具备条件的乡镇都通了公路 ■运建设规模和发展速度达到建国以来最平 ■西部交通实现了跨越式发展",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.01839748244977003,
      0.25894897182025894,
      0.35197288792060033,
      0.2762122366082762
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_9",
    "text": "一条主线：转变发展方式加快发展现代交通运输业，不断推动交通运输从传统向现代转型。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6124425078673444,
      0.2603029533722603,
      0.9648995400629388,
      0.27587374122027586
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_10",
    "text": "（一)基础设施建设迈上新台阶，为拉动经济增长做出重要贡献 “五”时期交通运输建设统计数据",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.014040183974824498,
      0.28365913514428365,
      0.373759380295328,
      0.3208936278243209
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_11",
    "text": "个王攻万问：调整交通运输结构—努推进综合运输体系建设,促进现代物流发展,提升科 技进步和信息化水平，建设资源节约型环境友好型行业，提高安全监管和应急处置能力。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6129266521423384,
      0.2911060336802911,
      0.9832970225127088,
      0.3104002707963104
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_14",
    "text": "六项重点任务：",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.6143790849673203,
      0.32123212321232125,
      0.6995884773662552,
      0.33544892950833544
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_12",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "table",
    "bbox": [
      0.026143790849673203,
      0.3256325632563256,
      0.36504478334543694,
      0.4522298383684522
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 14
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_13",
    "text": "八坝只仕分：第，围绕坚持扩内需战略,进一步调整和优化交通运输结构；第,围绕推进 农业现代化，继续推进农村交通基础设施建设；第三，围绕发展现代产业，加快综合运输体系和现代物流发展； 第四，围绕促进区域协调发展和城镇化，推进交通运输一体化；第五，围绕加快建设“两型社会”，大力发展低碳、 绿色、可持续交通运输；第六，围绕建设和谐社会，促进安全发展，着力提升交通运输安全应急保障能力。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6134107964173323,
      0.3273250401963273,
      0.9828128782377148,
      0.3618515697723618
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 15
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_15",
    "text": "一条建设原则：交通运输适度超前发展。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6153473735173082,
      0.37234492680037234,
      0.7872185911401598,
      0.3872387238723872
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 16
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_16",
    "text": "四个推进重点：",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.6134107964173323,
      0.39874756706439873,
      0.6995884773662552,
      0.412964373360413
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 17
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_17",
    "text": "四推进点：第，统筹规划衔接，建综合运输规划体系；",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6153473735173082,
      0.40484048404840484,
      0.8671023965141612,
      0.4126258779724126
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 18
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_18",
    "text": "第二，合理配置资源，调整优化通道资源，促进综合运输枢纽合理布局和各种运输方式优势互补，逐步实 现各种运输方式“无缝衔接”； 第三，加强多式联运等综合运输政策和标准规范研究制定和推广应用； 第四，推进综合运输管理和公共信息服务平台建设，逐步实现信息资源共享。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6129266521423384,
      0.41465685030041466,
      0.981360445412733,
      0.4474909029364475
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 19
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_21",
    "text": "三个主要问题",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.6143790849673203,
      0.4583227553524583,
      0.6976519002662793,
      0.47253956164847255
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 20
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_22",
    "text": "个要题：在新时期、新的发展阶段,交通运输业存在的问题主要表现在3个：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6148632292423142,
      0.4637386815604637,
      0.9513435003631082,
      0.4722010662604722
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 21
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_19",
    "text": "(二)运输服务再上新水平,显著改善了人民群众安全便捷出条件",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.016945049624788187,
      0.4644156723364644,
      0.3718228031953522,
      0.48134044173648133
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 22
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_23",
    "text": "第一，总量不足。东部地区逐步出现拥堵现象的同时，中部地区的局部路段也开始出现堵塞，西部的车 流量则快速上升。这说明交通的短缺问题还没有根本解决。随着国家的城镇化建设、区域化产业战略的转 移，客流货流的需求还会成倍上升，预计到2020年，交通的需求量将是现在的2倍多；",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6124425078673444,
      0.47355504781247354,
      0.9823287339627209,
      0.49792671574849795
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 23
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_20",
    "text": "交通运输总量对（2010/2005） 300 600 250 500 200 400- 100 50 0 公路货运 公路客运 沿海港口 内河货运 民航客运 民航货运 量/吨 量亿人货物吞吐量/亿量亿人 量/万吨 量/亿吨 2010年 220 300 61 17 2.66 570 2005年 138 167 34 11 1.4 312",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.019365770999757927,
      0.49488025725649487,
      0.19268942144759138,
      0.5700262333925701
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 24
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_33",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "picture",
    "bbox": [
      0.2067296054224159,
      0.49555724803249557,
      0.38925199709513436,
      0.5700262333925701
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 25
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_24",
    "text": "第二，结构不合理。就是各种运输方式的比较优势还没发挥出来，社会物流成本中交通运输费用的比 重还比较高，交通运输效率也还比较低。没有按照货物的特点，选择合适的运输方式，做到“宜路则路，宜水 则水，宜空则空”；",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6134107964173323,
      0.4986037065244986,
      0.9828128782377148,
      0.5233138698485233
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 26
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_25",
    "text": "第三，衔接不顺畅。特别是一些大城市发展中的综合交通枢纽建设问题，要从规划上统筹，从宏观上加 大协调力度，不能再各自为政。目前的现状离“旅客零换乘”和“货物无缝衔接”的要求还有比较大的差距。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6134107964173323,
      0.523990860624524,
      0.9828128782377148,
      0.5409156300245409
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 27
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_26",
    "text": "凹坝对佰地：是加快完善交通基础设施络,加速公路“断头路”的建设度,提升国省 干线公路网的通行能力；",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6129266521423384,
      0.5575019040365575,
      0.9832970225127088,
      0.574088178048574
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 28
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_29",
    "text": "二是着力推进综合运输体系的建设，在调整运输结构、加快枢纽建设、推进“多式联运”上下功夫； 三是着力推进科技进步和信息化建设，运用科技和信息化手段提升交通运输系统的利用效率、运行质 量、安全性能和服务水平；",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6134107964173323,
      0.5751036642125751,
      0.9832970225127088,
      0.5998138275365998
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 29
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_28",
    "text": "“十五”末翻了番,邮政普遍服务保障显著增 强，快递服务实现跨越式发展。现代运输组织形 式快速发展。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.20527717259743403,
      0.5784886180925785,
      0.3824739772452191,
      0.6035372768046036
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 30
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_27",
    "text": "城市公共客运能力快速增长，农村客运网络 进一步延伸，全国乡镇、建制村通班车率分别为 97%、87%。邮政业务总量年均增速达到17%，比",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.01888162672476398,
      0.5788271134805788,
      0.19511014282256112,
      0.6038757721926039
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 31
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_30",
    "text": "四是着力构建低碳交通运输体系，为转变发展方式，推进现代交通运输业发展提供有力支撑和保障。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6187363834422658,
      0.6004908183126005,
      0.9731299927378358,
      0.6082762122366083
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 32
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_31",
    "text": "(三)交通安全应急保障能力得到有效提升,在应对重大突发事 件中发挥了生命线作用",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.017913338174776083,
      0.6113226707286114,
      0.39070442992011617,
      0.6438182279766438
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 33
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_32",
    "text": "综合交通运输体系建设",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.6521423384168482,
      0.6180925784886181,
      0.9586056644880174,
      0.6414487602606415
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 34
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_35",
    "text": "5年间，中国海上搜救中心已成功救助遇险人员 97367人，平均一年救助超过19000人，救助成功率达到 96.3%。有效应对了南方低温雨雪冰冻灾害、汛期洪涝",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.01839748244977003,
      0.6512651265126512,
      0.19849915274751875,
      0.676990776000677
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 35
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_40",
    "text": "综合运输体系是各种运输方式在现代经济条件 下共同组成的布局合理、优势互补、分工明确、衔接 顺畅的运行系统和服务系统。从交通运输适应国民 经济发展的需求看，现有交通运输体系还存在总量 不足，东、中、西部地区发展不平衡，运输效率不高， 各种运输方式衔接不畅等问题，必须用推进综合运 输体系建设作为抓手，把快速发展的各种单一的运 输形式综合起来，优势才能互补。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6134107964173323,
      0.6512651265126512,
      0.7930283224400871,
      0.717948717948718
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 36
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_42",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.803679496489954,
      0.6512651265126512,
      0.9832970225127088,
      0.7433358720487433
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 37
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_36",
    "text": "灾害与冬季强降雪等影响，特别是在重大突发事件中，交 通运输发挥了重要的生命线作用。在北京奥运会、上海 世博会、广州亚运会中圆满完成了保通保运保安全任务。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.21011861534737353,
      0.6516036219006516,
      0.3897361413701283,
      0.676990776000677
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 38
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_37",
    "text": "（四)行业科技创新取得新进展，自主创新能力显著增强，信息化 水平明显提高",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.01839748244977003,
      0.6851146653126852,
      0.39070442992011617,
      0.7162562410087162
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 39
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_41",
    "text": "经过改革开放30年的建设，我国公路、铁路、 民航、水运、管道单个运输方式实现跨越式发展。 公路通车总里程由改革开放初期1980年的89万 公里到今年年底可达395万公里，居世界第二位； 内河航运通航里程由1980年的10.9万公里发展到 今年年底，预计达到12.3万公里，居世界第一；港 口货物和集装箱吞吐量连续7年居世界第一，预计 今年年底达到80亿吨和1亿4000多万TEU；民航 运输总周转量从改革开放初期的37位跃居世界第 二；公路货运量由改革初期1980年的14亿吨，世 界第六位跃居世界第一，预计到今年年底达到240 亿吨。交通运输瓶颈制约有所缓解，几种单一的 交通运输方式基本上都居世界前列。这些成就都 为构建综合运输体系打下了坚实基础。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6138949406923263,
      0.7186257087247186,
      0.7935124667150811,
      0.7436743674367436
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 40
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_38",
    "text": "节能减排初见成效，营运车船的运输周转量 能耗分别“五”末下降了5%和7%，资源节约 利用、集约利用和循环利用效率显著提高，交通建 设生态保护力度大大加强。党的建设和行业文明 建设取得新成效，为交通运输科学发展提供了强 大精神动力和政治保证。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.01839748244977003,
      0.7196411948887197,
      0.19849915274751875,
      0.745028348988745
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 41
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_39",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.21011861534737353,
      0.7196411948887197,
      0.39022028564512223,
      0.745028348988745
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 42
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_43",
    "text": "压题图：上为“苏通长江公路大桥”雄姿；下为浙江农村通畅便捷的乡村公路。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6666666666666666,
      0.7538292290767539,
      0.9295570079883806,
      0.761953118388762
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 43
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_44",
    "text": "重点建设工程项目(部分)",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.019849915274751877,
      0.7646610814927647,
      0.25950133139675624,
      0.7836168232207836
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 44
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_46",
    "text": "农村公路发展前所末有",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.5219075284434762,
      0.7836168232207836,
      0.9261679980634229,
      0.8140814081408141
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 45
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_45",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "table",
    "bbox": [
      0.01646090534979424,
      0.7968181433527968,
      0.38828370854514643,
      0.9494795633409495
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 46
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_54",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "picture",
    "bbox": [
      0.7049140643911885,
      0.8188203435728189,
      0.9891067538126361,
      0.9748667174409749
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 47
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_47",
    "text": "“十一五”时期，农村公路投资规 模年均增长30%，到“十一五”期末，全 国农村公路里程已达到345万公里，新 增里程53.5万公里，东中部地区94% 的建制村通沥青（水泥）路，西部98% 的建制村通公路，圆满完成“十一五” 农村公路建设目标任务。建设成就前 所未有，作用效果深刻鲜明：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.4173323650447833,
      0.8225437928408226,
      0.5519244734931009,
      0.8888888888888888
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 48
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_51",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.561123214717986,
      0.8225437928408226,
      0.6957153231663036,
      0.8557163408648557
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 49
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_52",
    "text": "建立了现代生活方式。农村公路 拉近了城乡时空距离，城乡交流日益 频繁，城市文明向乡村延伸，农民群众 接受现代文明，很多地方在农村公路 修通后，组织开展了改水、改电、改房、 改厕、垃圾污水处理等工程，改善了农 村居住环境，也促使传统乡村生活向 现代城市生活转变。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5620915032679739,
      0.8563933316408564,
      0.6957153231663036,
      0.9223999323009224
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 50
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_48",
    "text": "促进了农民增收。农村交通条件的 改善，拉近了农村和市场的距离，有效解 决了农产品运输难、销售难、货损大、成本 高、价格低的问题，农民增收效果明显。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.41830065359477125,
      0.8895658796648895,
      0.550956184943113,
      0.9227384276889228
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 51
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_49",
    "text": "改变了农村消费结构。近几年，各 类家用电器越来越多地进入了农家，摩 托车和农用车的销售也呈明显上升趋 势。不少农村家庭，还购买了小汽车。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.4173323650447833,
      0.9230769230769231,
      0.551440329218107,
      0.9562494711009563
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 52
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_53",
    "text": "加快了城乡一体化进程。农村公 路的快速发展，缩短了与城市间的距 离，许多农村青年白天到城市打工或 经商，傍晚乘坐客运班车回村居住，生 产生活方式向城市化转变，有效带动 了城乡一体化的快速发展。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5620915032679739,
      0.9234154184649234,
      0.6952311788913096,
      0.9728357451129729
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 53
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_50",
    "text": "推动了农村产业结构调整。便利 的农村交通条件，拉近了城乡间的距离， 加快不同地区间的信息交流和物资交 流，促进了传统农业向高效生态农业、绿 色旅游农业、商品加工业的转变，有效推 动了农村经济产业结构调整。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.4187847978697652,
      0.9565879664889566,
      0.5519244734931009,
      0.9731742405009731
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1",
    "order": 54
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_a9c9e3816aa5cb6866d02c10273dc665_1_34",
    "text": "本版文字内容、图片均由交通运输部提供",
